call - ed file
if file specified, load it into buffer, update default filename
start in command mode

commands

i - insert data into buffer, if there are data already, it will be rewritten
a - append data to the end of buffer
. - in insert mode, return to command mode
w file - write buffer to file, if no file specified, default is used
e file - read file to buffer, update default filename, if no file specified, default is used
p - print buffer to console
C - switch color mode
q - quit
